Class MoneroTransferRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • monero.wallet.model.MoneroTransfer

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Filter<MoneroTransfer>

    public class MoneroTransferRequest
extends MoneroTransfer
implements Filter<MoneroTransfer>
    Configures a request to retrieve transfers. All transfers are returned except those that do not meet the criteria defined in this request.
